       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. REWRITE-DEMO.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT IO-FILE ASSIGN TO "data.dat"
               ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       FD IO-FILE.
       01 IO-REC PIC X(20).
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           OPEN OUTPUT IO-FILE
           MOVE "Original" TO IO-REC
           WRITE IO-REC
           CLOSE IO-FILE
           DISPLAY "Written"
           STOP RUN.
